{"tid":2446254,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄉議局預備變condom??","createTime":"2021-03-14T10:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T11:20:12.000Z","uid":259520,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e6996262e2ca72af88089a2c90135182c3b429d7","tid":2446254,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:10:31.000Z","msg":"鄉議局預備變condom??<br />\n<br />\n選委會無提有鄉議局份. 港共明顯開始著手攪丁權.<br />\n你知777幾咁方仗.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210313/s00002/1615572346819/%E3%80%8C%E6%9D%91%E5%B1%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210313%2Fs00002%2F1615572346819%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%259D%2591%25E5%25B1%258B&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfCbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=8dc117ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210313%2Fs00002%2F1615572346819%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%259D%2591%25E5%25B1%258B&h=12293d02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210313/s00002/1615572346819/%E3%80%8C%E6%9D%91%E5%B1%8B</a><br />\n%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B%E3%80%8D%E7%8E%8B%E5%85%89%E6%A6%AE%E8%88%87%E5%AD%90%E6%B6%89%E5%A5%97%E4%B8%81%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E6%8B%9824%E4%BA%BA-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%95%86%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%8B%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA<br />\n<br />\n「村屋大王」王光榮與子涉套丁被捕 廉署證實拘24人 包括地產發展商及丁屋申請人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210314/s00001/1615697149546/%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-%E8%AD%9A%E8%80%80%E5%AE%97%E6%96%995%E6%9C%88%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%B3%95%E4%BE%8B%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210314%2F